# HuggingFace API Token
# Required for downloading models from HuggingFace Hub
# Get your token from: https://huggingface.co/settings/tokens
HF_TOKEN=your_huggingface_token_here

# Instructions:
# 1. Copy this file to .env: cp .env.example .env
# 2. Replace 'your_huggingface_token_here' with your actual HuggingFace token
# 3. Never commit the .env file to version control (it's in .gitignore)
#
# To get a HuggingFace token:
# 1. Create an account at https://huggingface.co/
# 2. Go to Settings > Access Tokens
# 3. Create a new token with 'read' permissions
# 4. Copy the token and paste it above
#
# Note: The token is required for:
# - Downloading Llama-3-8B model (meta-llama/Meta-Llama-3-8B-Instruct)
# - Downloading IndoBERT models (if not using local fine-tuned model)